## Disclaimer Regarding *Command & Conquer: Tiberian Sun* Assets

This project includes derivative works created to resemble assets from *Command & Conquer: Tiberian Sun*, which is the intellectual property of Westwood Studios and Electronic Arts (EA). 

**No original assets from *Command & Conquer: Tiberian Sun* are distributed in this repository.** For certain game features, users will need to extract original assets from their legally obtained copy of *Command & Conquer: Tiberian Sun*. 

